  <div class="not-prose mb-6 rounded-lg border border-cream-border bg-cream-muted px-5 py-4">
    <p class="text-text-body">
      <strong class="text-text-heading">These instructions are for the Q-Tune Solder Kit (Through-Hole)</strong>, the kit with loose components you solder onto the board. Building the standard,
